type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

! Settings

!! Engine Selection

Select the graph engine in the tw-graph plugin settings:

''ControlPanel > Settings > Graph Engine > Cytoscape''

Or set the config tiddler directly:

|!Tiddler |`$:/config/flibbles/graph/engine` |
|!Value |`Cytoscape` |

!! Cluster Configuration

Each graph can store its cluster config in a separate tiddler via the `clusterData` graph property:

```
<$properties $for="graph" clusterData="$:/config/my-app/clusters">
```

Multiple graphs can share the same config tiddler for synchronized clusters, or use different tiddlers for independent grouping.

!! Compound Node Styling

Cluster containers render with:

* Dashed round-rectangle border
* Semi-transparent background (12% opacity)
* Bold label at top inside the container
* Minimum 120×80px size when empty

Colors are configurable per cluster via double-click → color picker.
